Job Description
ZXMCO Pakistan (Pvt) Ltd. is the fastest growing brand in the motorcycle manufacturing Industry with a national and international sales network. We are looking for young, dedicated and seasoned professionals for the following positions at our plant and regional office in Lahore.
1- Production Manager: No.1
- Have Experience of CNC
- B.E. Mech / Manf.
- Raiwind, Lahore
- 5 Years minimum experience
2- Country Manager Business Development: No.1
- MBA (Marketing)
- Raiwind, Lahore
- 7 years minimum experience
3- Executive (Credit Receivables): No.4
- MBA (Marketing)
- Lahore & Multan
- 2 years
4- Executive (Sales): No.4
- MBA (Marketing)
- Lahore & Multan
- 2 Years minimum experience
Preference shall be given to candidates with experience in the Auto Industry.
Only short listed candidates will be contacted.
Competitive compensation will be given to the right candidate.Apply Instructions for This Job
Please email your resume or send by post not later than 4th May, 2014, mentioning the position applied for in subject line/cover letter.
